<http://syn.org/gdc/MultiplexMicroscopy/tumor_tissue_type> <http://syn.org/node> <http://syn.org/gdc/MultiplexMicroscopy>;
  <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tumor_tissue_type";
